e]] [[Gitanes]]\n| [[Matra-Simca MS670|Matra-Simca MS670C]] \n| {{Goodyear}}\n| 337\n| 4606.571&nbsp;km\n| [[World Sportscar Championship|World Championship for Makes]]\n|-\n! [[1975 24 Hours of Le Mans|1975]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Jacky Ickx]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Derek Bell (racing driver)|Derek Bell]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Gulf Racing|Gulf Research Racing Co.]]\n| [[Mirage (race car)|Mirage]] GR8-[[Ford Motor Company|Ford]] [[Cosworth]]\n| {{Goodyear}}\n| 336\n| 4594.577&nbsp;km\n|\n|-\n! [[1976 24 Hours of Le Mans|1976]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Jacky Ickx]]<br>{{flagicon|NLD}} [[Gijs van Lennep]]\n| {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Martini Racing]] [[Porsche|Porsche System]]\n| [[Porsche 936]]\n| {{Goodyear}}\n| 349\n| 4769.923&nbsp;km\n|\n|-\n! [[1977 24 Hours of Le Mans|1977]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Jacky Ickx]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Hurley Haywood]]<br>{{flagicon|FRG}} [[J\u00fcrgen Barth]]\n| {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Martini Racing]] [[Porsche|Porsche System]]\n| [[Porsche 936|Porsche 936/77]]\n| {{Dunlop}}\n| 342\n| 4671.83&nbsp;km\n|\n|-\n! [[1978 24 Hours of Le Mans|1978]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean-Pierre Jaussaud]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Didier Pironi]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Alpine Renault]]\n| [[Renault Alpine A442|Renault Alpine A442B]]\n| {{Michelin}}\n| 369\n| 5044.53&nbsp;km\n|\n|-\n! [[1979 24 Hours of Le Mans|1979]]\n| {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Klaus Ludwig]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Bill Whittington]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Don Whittington]]\n| {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Porsche]] [[Kremer Racing]]\n| [[Porsche 935|Porsche 935 K3]]\n| {{Dunlop}}\n| 307\n| 4173.93&nbsp;km\n|\n|-\n! [[1980 24 Hours of Le Mans|1980]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean Rondeau]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean-Pierre Jaussaud]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean Rondeau]]\n| [[Jean Rondeau|Rondeau]] M379B-[[Ford Motor Company|Ford]] [[Cosworth]]\n| {{Goodyear}}\n| 338\n| 4608.02&nbsp;km\n| [[World Sportscar Championship|World Championship for Makes]]\n|-\n! [[1981 24 Hours of Le Mans|1981]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Jacky Ickx]]<br